One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. *** VA ASSUMABLE LOAN 3.5%*** Welcome to this stunning 3-bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom, and 2-car garage home nestled in a gated community. As you enter, you'll be greeted by a beautiful chandelier, setting the tone for the elegance that awaits.    This home boasts an updated kitchen, complete with modern appliances and plenty of storage space for all your culinary needs. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, featuring a renovated ensuite bathroom that is sure to impress.    Convenience abounds with a laundry room, ensuring those everyday tasks are a breeze. The new garage door opener and slider for the garage door enhance functionality and add a touch of sophistication.    Outdoor entertaining is a delight, thanks to the spacious lanai and inviting pool. Whether you're lounging by the pool or hosting a barbeque, this backyard oasis provides the perfect backdrop for creating lasting memories.    Location is key, and this home delivers. Positioned close to the expressway, commuting is a breeze, making this home ideal for those on the go.    Don't let this opportunity slip away to own this exquisite home in a coveted community. Call today for your private showing and embark on your new chapter of luxury living. New Roof in 2021 with warranty!
